{"tid":498772,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[GOT] 珊莎讚《權力遊戲》第八季大結局 全員鼓掌當場淚奔","createTime":"2017-12-14T06:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T09:10:44.000Z","uid":72478,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8a86e3bbdfa0fb629f6aa3a5052b5295140daa62","tid":498772,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imagesvc.timeincapp.com/v3/fan/image?url=https://winteriscoming.net/wp-content/blogs.dir/385/files/2017/08/Screen-Shot-2017-08-07-at-4.38.30-PM.jpg&amp;c=sc&amp;w=699&amp;h=455\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagesvc.timeincapp.com%2Fv3%2Ffan%2Fimage%3Furl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwinteriscoming.net%2Fwp-content%2Fblogs.dir%2F385%2Ffiles%2F2017%2F08%2FScreen-Shot-2017-08-07-at-4.38.30-PM.jpg%26c%3Dsc%26w%3D699%26h%3D455&h=f443eae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在《權力的遊戲》中扮演珊莎的演員索菲&middot;特納是最新的&ldquo;罪人&rdquo;，她在接受《好萊塢報導》的採訪時透露了之前她與主創聚在一起朗讀最後一集劇本時的經歷。<br />\n<br />\n   &ldquo;在最後一個劇本的末尾，他們大聲念道：《權力的遊戲》完結了！（End of Game of Thrones）。這句話一喊出來，幾乎每個人都止不住流淚，當一個人開始鼓掌時，我們都跟著開始鼓掌歡呼，感覺真是太棒了。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  雖然特納並沒有透露《權力的遊戲》大結局的信息，但她也在現場是否意味著珊莎活到了最後？不過當然，也可能是朗讀會主持人也要求第八季&ldquo;已死&rdquo;的角色也參加活動到最後。此外特納還暗示，在第八季會有更大的人物關係圖，有更多人登場，更多的陰謀和聯盟。而且因為夜王的正式參戰，奇幻元素會越來越多，包括戰斗等事物都開始朝向奇幻史詩發展。而且因為角色驅動故事會讓史詩感更加明顯。<br />\n<br />\n   特納還表示，演員們也和觀眾粉絲一樣會猜測各種走向和劇情，每個人都在討論將會發生的事，誰會死誰會活到最後之類的。然後現在他們已經知道了，這種揭曉答案的感覺非常奇妙，也非常棒。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://games.sina.com.cn/g/g/2017-12-14/fypsvkp2951685.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgames.sina.com.cn%2Fg%2Fg%2F2017-12-14%2Ffypsvkp2951685.shtml&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=93cfb44d\" target=\"_blank\">http://games.sina.com.cn/g/g/2017-12-14/fypsvkp2951685.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://winteriscoming.net/2017/12/13/sophie-turner-the-whole-cast-burst-into-tears-after-season-8-table-read/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwinteriscoming.net%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2Fsophie-turner-the-whole-cast-burst-into-tears-after-season-8-table-read%2F&d=vFomSXGlPjIjNwwJfx9yWE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=cd789402\" target=\"_blank\">https://winteriscoming.net/2017/12/13/sophie-turner-the-whole-cast-burst-into-tears-after-season-8-table-read/</a>"},{"pid":"d52033d9175a9c004ecb3aa10ed0b98933b2b2e0","tid":498772,"uid":124450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:07:35.000Z","msg":"唔是馬丁落筆 不了"},{"pid":"9ac68e43c2217e4c70a617b047b561294226e6bc","tid":498772,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:08:40.000Z","msg":"總覺得sansa會死<br />\n啲狼同主人命運掛勾<br />\n應該死剩侏儒 arya Sam"},{"pid":"faa12997a70d44e42bc8af00b8b7d1b8d4e5702d","tid":498772,"uid":65328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ac68e43c2217e4c70a617b047b561294226e6bc","tid":498772,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:08:40.000Z","msg":"總覺得sansa會死<br />\n啲狼同主人命運掛勾<br />\n應該死剩侏儒 arya Sam"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:53:50.000Z","msg":"如果係就一早死左"},{"pid":"bf8dc7197d924ecd46d4050e61ae09605e2099f4","tid":498772,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"faa12997a70d44e42bc8af00b8b7d1b8d4e5702d","tid":498772,"uid":65328,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ac68e43c2217e4c70a617b047b561294226e6bc","tid":498772,"uid":41629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:08:40.000Z","msg":"總覺得sansa會死<br />\n啲狼同主人命運掛勾<br />\n應該死剩侏儒 arya Sam"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T02:53:50.000Z","msg":"如果係就一早死左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"唔俾之後先死？"},{"pid":"071a06d3ec51a58de73babf992dd1354ac169895","tid":498772,"uid":66839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"幾時敏? 我HBO到今年11月完"},{"pid":"11182cacd6bb161e36e96871b8364a5097e1024d","tid":498772,"uid":34779,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01